PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Product Discovery App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the app find new products?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app uses advanced algorithms to scour the internet for the latest product releases across various categories. We analyze data from e-commerce sites, social media, blogs, and more to identify trending and newly launched products.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I filter products by category or price range?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, absolutely. Our app allows you to set filters based on product categories, price ranges, and other preferences to curate a personalized feed of new products tailored to your interests.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How often is the product feed updated?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Our product feed is updated in real-time, ensuring that you always have access to the most recent and up-to-date information about new product launches across various industries.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is the app available on multiple platforms?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our app is available on both iOS and Android devices, as well as a web-based platform accessible from any internet-connected device, allowing you to discover new products anytime, anywhere.
HERO_SUBTITLE: Stay ahead of the curve by exploring cutting-edge offerings
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app is designed to help you find and explore the latest products on the market, from cutting-edge gadgets to innovative household items.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How does the product discovery work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We curate a constantly updated list of newly released products across various categories. You can browse through them, read detailed descriptions, and see customer reviews.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I filter products by category?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, absolutely! You can easily filter products based on categories like technology, home & living, fashion, and more to find what interests you most.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How can I stay updated on new product launches?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: You can enable push notifications to receive alerts whenever exciting new products are added to our app. You'll never miss out on the latest releases!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Is there a way to save products I'm interested in?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Definitely! You can create a wishlist or favorites list to save products you'd like to purchase or keep an eye on for future reference.
